videos.title: It Only Takes 10 Gates to Win the Game  $100 Budget Magic
videos.description:
Maze's End is back in Standard for the first time in forever! Let's load up on Gates and see if we can make it work on a $100 budget!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish
